{"name":"以为感悟生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/categories/以为感悟生活/","url":"/async/categories/以为感悟生活.json","count":15,"_total":15,"_totalPage":2,"_page":2,"posts":[{"tags":[{"name":"生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/生活/","url":"/async/tags/生活.json","count":9},{"name":"老文","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/老文/","url":"/async/tags/老文.json","count":8},{"name":"感悟","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/感悟/","url":"/async/tags/感悟.json","count":8}],"categories":[{"name":"以为感悟生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/categories/以为感悟生活/","url":"/async/categories/以为感悟生活.json","count":15}],"url":"/async/posts/2016/03/14/老了也很美.json","date":1458002681000,"path":{"year":2016,"month":3,"day":14,"name":"老了也很美"},"title":"老了，也很美","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/2016/03/14/老了也很美/","content":"<ul>\n<li>此文献给《飞屋环游记》和《暗恋桃花源》</li>\n</ul>\n<p>久闻话剧《暗恋桃花源》大名，却始终没能一睹其风采，今天无意之间在偶像来了最后一期中，看到了其中的一个片段，汪涵不愧是博采众长，虽是话剧的处女秀，但表现出来的情绪透过冷冷的屏幕也感动着每一个人。<br>"},{"tags":[{"name":"生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/生活/","url":"/async/tags/生活.json","count":9},{"name":"老文","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/老文/","url":"/async/tags/老文.json","count":8},{"name":"感悟","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/感悟/","url":"/async/tags/感悟.json","count":8}],"categories":[{"name":"以为感悟生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/categories/以为感悟生活/","url":"/async/categories/以为感悟生活.json","count":15}],"url":"/async/posts/2016/03/14/黑暗面.json","date":1458002183000,"path":{"year":2016,"month":3,"day":14,"name":"黑暗面"},"title":"黑暗面（死亡笔记&冰血暴S1&忠奸人）","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/2016/03/14/黑暗面/","content":"<p>拖沓了近三周，终于在真正意义上看完了一部动漫——死亡笔记。第一次接触这部作品应该是在大学本科期间，当时同学推荐的是电影版本，看完之后只是觉得很新奇，果然日本的动漫总是会有一些很奇怪的想法，"},{"tags":[{"name":"梦境","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/梦境/","url":"/async/tags/梦境.json","count":2}],"categories":[{"name":"以为感悟生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/categories/以为感悟生活/","url":"/async/categories/以为感悟生活.json","count":15}],"url":"/async/posts/2016/08/12/爷爷.json","date":1471011898000,"path":{"year":2016,"month":8,"day":12,"name":"爷爷"},"title":"爷爷","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/2016/08/12/爷爷/","content":"<p>今早梦见了爷爷。"},{"tags":[{"name":"写文","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/写文/","url":"/async/tags/写文.json","count":1}],"categories":[{"name":"以为感悟生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/categories/以为感悟生活/","url":"/async/categories/以为感悟生活.json","count":15}],"url":"/async/posts/2016/08/31/缘.json","date":1472628517000,"path":{"year":2016,"month":8,"day":31,"name":"缘"},"title":"缘","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/2016/08/31/缘/","content":"<p>一篇文章，无论是我们通过键盘噼里啪啦敲出来的，还是埋头苦干奋笔疾书写出来的，当我落下第一个字的那一刹那，你我便结下了这一生的不解之缘。"},{"tags":[{"name":"回忆","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/tags/回忆/","url":"/async/tags/回忆.json","count":1}],"categories":[{"name":"以为感悟生活","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/categories/以为感悟生活/","url":"/async/categories/以为感悟生活.json","count":15}],"url":"/async/posts/2016/09/01/细雨.json","date":1472790520000,"path":{"year":2016,"month":9,"day":1,"name":"细雨"},"title":"细雨","permalink":"http://www.smartyi8979.com/2016/09/01/细雨/","content":"<p>事情是这样的，今晚回到家吃完饭在洗碗的时候，不小心将水龙头堵了一下，于是水龙头中水向四处溅开，在我的衣服上留下了点点水滴，我看见衣服上挂着的水珠，脸上竟然笑了出来。"}]}